name: Shokumotsu Cube
description:
[3500x3500px]


This cube provides a variety of traditional Japanese food. Dango, Ramen, Wasabi Ice Cream, Coffee Drink, Donuts, Ichigo Juice, Takoyaki, Sushi, Dorayaki, Onigiri, Taiyaki, Kaarage, Yakiniku, Tempura, Tamagoyaki, Oshiruko.


I'll visit this cube in the Metaverse World. maybe to try traditional Japanese Ramen or even Wasabi Ice Cream
